1 The Legislature, by joint resolution, may appoint one or more of
2 its members to intervene as a matter of right in any case in which
3 the constitutionality or enforceability of this act is challenged.
4 SECTION 6. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
5 Passed the House of Representatives the 9th day of March, 2026.
